    "body": "This is a problem for me as well. I wish there was a way of specifying multiple \"root\" directories.\r\n\r\nMy current workaround is to link the google include path into my protobufs directory, and call ```grpc.load({ file: <filePath>, root: ROOT_PROTO_PATH})```"
