    "created_at": "2018-05-10T17:20:43Z",
    "updated_at": "2018-05-10T17:20:43Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I would like to note that the `@grpc/proto-loader` also solves the problem described in the title of this issue. One of the options is `includeDirs`, which is an array of strings listing any number of include paths.\r\n\r\nThe quoted code does not need to use that option because the proto loader library also depends on a more recent version of Protobuf.js that automatically includes `google/protobuf/*.proto` in its include path."
  },
